page.title: 12H.M.S.SULTAN,GOSPORT.
page.content: {H.M.S Sultan}is the{Royal Navy {Engineering School}in Military Road Gosport.It is 30-40 years old.It trains people to be engineers on ships and naval aircraft etc.My name is David Newbery and I live at 91 Charden Road, Rowner, Gosport, Hants PO13 OEE.I was 11 years old on the 7th of February 1985.My mum works at H.M.S Sultan in the main dining hall for {M.O.D.}She likes the people who she works with and sometimes she even likes her boss.' She gets 72 hours holiday a week and she has to work for 20 hours a week. Mum works in the main dining hall and she does shift work. She does cleaning,washing dishes and waitressing.She leaves for work at 6.10 a.m. and gets home at 9.40 a.m. Then she leaves again at 4.40 p.m. and gets home at 7.10 p.m.
